description: I cant say that I hate shopping malls - today I´ve had a business meeting there. So I´ve decided to mix the business with pleasure and take my camera with me. Accidentally I switched the cam on just close to the gym. In a few seconds I´ve spotted a young dude leaving the gym. I knew this one would be a real catch, if I persuade him successfully. Smiling and talkative pal from Slovakia who lived in Poland for his whole life. Came to Prague to find a job. I knew he is gonna need cash. Didn´t take too long and he showed me his penis, just there while people been passing by. I didn´t just offered him a tidy sum of money but as well a new experience. Cause I guessed right that he was an adventurous one. Enjoy the fun I´ve had with him in a small nearby hotel room.
title: Czech Hunter 165
